casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Mingo, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Mingo (1996), 74 Ohio St.3d 532.]

(No. 95-1780 Submitted December 12, 1995 Decided February 14, 1996.) Joseph T. Deters, Hamilton County Prosecuting Attorney, and Ronald W. Springman, Jr., Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. James H. Mingo, pro se. *533 Per Curiam.

We affirm the decision of the court of appeals for the reason stated in its entry.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
